## Environment variables

Please define and import all environment variables in your code from [settings.py](./src/{{ project_slug }}/core/settings.py) file like so: 

```python
class Settings(BaseSettings):
    """Load environment variables as settings."""
    
    MY_ENV_VARIABLE_1: str
    MY_ENV_VARIABLE_2: int = 5
```

During local development, use the .env file to set environment variables.